# EYS Design Rules

Visual direction:
- dark hero
- light content sections
- red CTAs
- black / charcoal / silver / white palette
- premium local contractor
- structured, angular, disciplined layouts

Avoid:
- cheap flyer look
- cartoon icons
- unrestrained gradients
- excessive animation
- crowded cards
- tiny mobile tap targets

Mobile:
- phone CTA must be easy to reach.
- tap targets at least 44px high.
- content must stack cleanly.
